# Graphs to NOT expand into a worktree on `libseq boot`.
#
# Every branch under graphs/* is treated as a graph by default. List a graph
# name here (the part after graphs/) to skip it — e.g. a template or an
# archived graph you don't want checked out on this device.
#
# One name per line. Blank lines and lines starting with # are ignored.
#
# Example:
# _sample
